* '''[[Mildenhall, Wiltshire|Mildenhall]]''', [[Wiltshire]] – {{IPAc-en|ˈ|m|ʌ|l|d|ən|h|ɔː|l}} besides intuitive<ref>[http://it.forvo.com/word/mildenhall/ Mildenhall audio pronunciation]</ref> 
*'''[[Mossley]]''', [[Greater Manchester]] - {{IPAc-en|ˈ|m|ɒ|z|l|i}}
