=== N===
[[File:Norwich_Skyline.jpg|thumb|[[Norwich]] is a cathedral city of more than 140,000 people and the county town of [[Norfolk]] which has more than 850,000 inhabitants.]]
* [[River Nene|River '''Nene''']], [[Northamptonshire]] – {{IPAc-en|n|ɛ|n}} (intuitive {{IPAc-en|n|iː|n}} also heard) <ref name=wells />
* '''[[Norwich]]''', [[Norfolk]] – {{IPAc-en|ˈ|n|ɒr|ᵻ|dʒ}} <ref name=wells />{{#tag:ref|Like Berwick, the fact of the "r" being pronounced with the last syllable negates an intuitive interpretation.  Many people outside of its area/history would have a very low chance of guessing this.|group= n}}

