* '''Plaistow''':
** [[Plaistow, Newham|Plaistow]], [[Greater London]] – {{IPAc-en|ˈ|p|l|ɑː|s|t|oʊ}}<ref name="Catherine SangsterLena Olausson2006">{{cite book| last1 = Sangster| first1 = Catherine| last2 = Olausson| first2 = Lena| title = Oxford BBC guide to pronunciation| year = 2006| publisher = Oxford University Press| location = Oxford, England| isbn = 0-19-280710-2| page = 300| quote = This is correct for the Plaistows in London and West Sussex. }}</ref>
** [[Plaistow, West Sussex]] – as above<ref name="Catherine SangsterLena Olausson2006" />
* '''[[Plymouth]]''', [[Devon]] – {{IPAc-en|ˈ|p|l|ɪ|m|ə|θ}}
* '''[[Pontefract]]''', [[West Yorkshire]] — {{IPAc-en|ˈ|p|ʌ|m|f|r|ɪ|t}} (traditional, currently intuitive {{IPAc-en|ˈ|p|ɒ|n|t|ə|f|r|æ|k|t}})
