* 1806 - British [[British invasions of the Río de la Plata|briefly in power]].
* 1810
** 18–25 May: [[May Revolution]].<ref name=WorldBook>{{citation |title=Timelines: History of Argentina from 1580 to 1983 |work=[[World Book Encyclopedia|World Book]] |location=USA |subscription=yes |accessdate=December 1, 2014 }}</ref>
** [[National Library of the Argentine Republic|State Library]] established.{{sfn|Mulhall|1869}}
